==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: cunnilingus
<hw>cun`ni*lin"gus</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL., fr. L.
<ets>cunnus</ets> vulva + <ets>lingere</ets> to lick.]</ety>
<def>Stimulation of the vulva or clitoris of one person by the tongue of
another, for the purpose of giving sexual gratification.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> cunnilinctus.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cunning</ent>⟦br⟧
